      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Commercial FEA codes (Ansys) used by all three modeling teams carry ISO 9001 quality management certification and FDA-recognized software validation documentation. Version control and audit trails confirmed for all simulation runs."
    },
    {
