    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team accepts this gap given that the single ASTM F1717 load condition is the condition specified in the regulatory submission and no additional load conditions are claimed. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the declared submission purpose.",
